	<div class="articleCorrection">

	
			<b>Correction:</b> July 1, 2006, Saturday

A theater entry in the Listings pages of Weekend yesterday about ''The House in Town,'' at the Mitzi E. Newhouse Theater, misstated the closing date. It is July 30, not tomorrow.
<p>	
	
	</div>

	


<img itemprop="newsUsageTag" src="http://analytics.apnewsregistry.com/analytics/v2/image.svc//RWS/nytimes.com/CAI/924962/E/prod/PC/Basic/AT/A" alt="" width="1" height="1" style="display:none;" />
</div>	</div>
