        <div class="story">
            <h6 class="kicker">
                                    <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/pages/national/index.html">U.S. &raquo;</a>
                            </h6>
            <div class="mothImage">
                <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/23/us/curlers-aim-sweep-to-a-win-over-the-heat.html"><img src="http://i1.nyt.com/images/2014/06/23/us/23MOTH_CURLING/23MOTH_CURLING-moth.jpg" alt="Curlers&rsquo; Aim: Sweep to a Win Over the Heat" width="151" height="151" /></a>
            </div>
            <h6 class="headline"><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/23/us/curlers-aim-sweep-to-a-win-over-the-heat.html">Curlers&rsquo; Aim: Sweep to a Win Over the Heat<i class="icon dot-logo-icon hidden"></i></a></h6>
        </div>
    </td>
                                                <td class="hidden">
